: 179.56, "text": " And we're going to say, what do you want to see in your writing?", "tokens": [50547, 400, 321, 434, 516, 281, 584, 11, 437, 360, 291, 528, 281, 536, 294, 428, 3579, 30, 50724], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12279775619506836, "compression_ratio": 1.8953488372093024, "no_speech_prob": 0.0033558602444827557}, {"id": 36, "seek": 17236, "start": 179.56, "end": 184.32000000000002, "text": " What do you want as a result in your writing in the area of stress?", "tokens": [50724, 708, 360, 291, 528, 382, 257, 1874, 294, 428, 3579, 294, 264, 1859, 295, 4244, 30, 50962], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12279775619506836, "compression_ratio": 1.8953488372093024, "no_speech_prob": 0.0033558602444827557}, {"id": 37, "seek": 17236, "start": 184.32000000000002, "end": 186.10000000000002, "text": " So write that down.", "tokens": [50962, 407, 2464, 300, 760, 13, 51051], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12279775619506836, "compression_ratio": 1.8953488372093024, "no_speech_prob": 0.0033558602444827557}, {"id": 38, "seek": 17236, "start": 186.10000000000002, "end": 190.86, "text": " So this could be, you know, I want to feel prepared.", "tokens": [51051, 407, 341, 727, 312, 11, 291, 458, 11, 286, 528, 281, 841, 4927, 13, 51289], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12279775619506836, "compression_ratio": 1.8953488372093024, "no_speech_prob": 0.0033558602444827557}, {"id": 39, "seek": 17236, "start": 190.86, "end": 194.64000000000001, "text": " I want to feel strong.", "tokens": [51289, 286, 528, 281, 841, 2068, 13, 51478], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12279775619506836, "compression_ratio": 1.8953488372093024, "no_speech_prob": 0.0033558602444827557}, {"id": 40, "seek": 17236, "start": 194.64000000000001, "end": 198.9, "text": " I want to feel capable.", "tokens": [51478, 286, 528, 281, 841, 8189, 13, 51691], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12279775619506836, "compression_ratio": 1.8953488372093024, "no_speech_prob": 0.0033558602444827557}, {"id": 41, "seek": 17236, "start": 198.9, "end": 201.94000000000003, "text": " I want to feel loose.", "tokens": [51691, 286, 528, 281, 841, 9612, 13, 51843], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12279775619506836, "compression_ratio": 1.8953488372093024, "no_speech_prob": 0.0033558602444827557}, {"id": 42, "seek": 20194, "start": 201.96, "end": 207.16, "text": " And here it is, you write that down, just a few things, like three to five things, write", "tokens": [50365, 400, 510, 309, 307, 11, 291, 2464, 300, 760, 11, 445, 257, 1326, 721, 11, 411, 1045, 281, 1732, 721, 11, 2464, 50625], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.21176259994506835, "compression_ratio": 1.6666666666666667, "no_speech_prob": 0.007560937199741602}, {"id": 43, "seek": 20194, "start": 207.16, "end": 209.68, "text": " it down.", "tokens": [50625, 309, 760, 13, 50751], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.21176259994506835, "compression_ratio": 1.6666666666666667, "no_speech_prob": 0.007560937199741602}, {"id": 44, "seek": 20194, "start": 209.68, "end": 213.6, "text": " Then after you've written that down, like I said, we're going to work backwards.", "tokens": [50751, 1396, 934, 291, 600, 3720, 300, 760, 11, 411, 286, 848, 11, 321, 434, 516, 281, 589, 12204, 13, 50947], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.21176259994506835, "compression_ratio": 1.6666666666666667, "no_speech_prob": 0.007560937199741602}, {"id": 45, "seek": 20194, "start": 213.6, "end": 219.0, "text": " We're going to see what belief would you have to have about stress in order to accomplish", "tokens": [50947, 492, 434, 516, 281, 536, 437, 7107, 576, 291, 362, 281, 362, 466, 4244, 294, 1668, 281, 9021, 51217], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.21176259994506835, "compression_ratio": 1.6666666666666667, "no_speech_prob": 0.007560937199741602}, {"id": 46, "seek": 20194, "start": 219.0, "end": 222.72, "text": " that goal.", "tokens": [51217, 300, 3387, 13, 51403], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.21176259994506835, "compression_ratio": 1.6666666666666667, "no_speech_prob": 0.007560937199741602}, {"id": 47, "seek": 20194, "start": 222.72, "end": 230.0, "text": " So for example, if you want to be loose in the saddle, you want to be relaxed and not", "tokens": [51403, 407, 337, 1365, 11, 498, 291, 528, 281, 312, 9612, 294, 264, 30459, 11, 291, 528, 281, 312, 14628, 293, 406, 51767], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.21176259994506835, "compression_ratio": 1.6666666666666667, "no_speech_prob": 0.007560937199741602}, {"id": 48, "seek": 23000, "start": 230.06, "end": 235.46, "text": " tense, your belief about stress has to be that stress is good for you.", "tokens": [50367, 18760, 11, 428, 7107, 466, 4244, 575, 281, 312, 300, 4244, 307, 665, 337, 291, 13, 50637], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11261825561523438, "compression_ratio": 1.7797356828193833, "no_speech_prob": 0.01332259364426136}, {"id": 49, "seek": 23000, "start": 235.46, "end": 241.58, "text": " There's a process in it and that you can let go and be relaxed in it.", "tokens": [50637, 821, 311, 257, 1399, 294, 309, 293, 300, 291, 393, 718, 352, 293, 312, 14628, 294, 309, 13, 50943], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11261825561523438, "compression_ratio": 1.7797356828193833, "no_speech_prob": 0.01332259364426136}, {"id": 50, "seek": 23000, "start": 241.58, "end": 244.94, "text": " So as you've written this out, what you've previously believed in, what it was serving", "tokens": [50943, 407, 382, 291, 600, 3720, 341, 484, 11, 437, 291, 600, 8046, 7847, 294, 11, 437, 309, 390, 8148, 51111], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11261825561523438, "compression_ratio": 1.7797356828193833, "no_speech_prob": 0.01332259364426136}, {"id": 51, "seek": 23000, "start": 244.94, "end": 253.14, "text": " you for, and then what you want out of it really, or the service that you want and what", "tokens": [51111, 291, 337, 11, 293, 550, 437, 291, 528, 484, 295, 309, 534, 11, 420, 264, 2643, 300, 291, 528, 293, 437, 51521], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11261825561523438, "compression_ratio": 1.7797356828193833, "no_speech_prob": 0.01332259364426136}, {"id": 52, "seek": 23000, "start": 253.14, "end": 259.38, "text": " belief you have to have to get there, all of a sudden we have a mindset change available", "tokens": [51521, 7107, 291, 362, 281, 362, 281, 483, 456, 11, 439, 295, 257, 3990, 321, 362, 257, 12543, 1319, 2435, 51833], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11261825561523438, "compression_ratio": 1.7797356828193833, "no_speech_prob": 0.01332259364426136}, {"id": 53, "seek": 25938, "start": 259.44, "end": 260.44, "text": " to you.", "tokens": [50367, 281, 291, 13, 50417], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12602580278769307, "compression_ratio": 1.7291666666666667, "no_speech_prob": 0.019321832805871964}, {"id": 54, "seek": 25938, "start": 260.44, "end": 264.71999999999997, "text": " So you have the opportunity now to believe one and get one result or believe the other", "tokens": [50417, 407, 291, 362, 264, 2650, 586, 281, 1697, 472, 293, 483, 472, 1874, 420, 1697, 264, 661, 50631], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12602580278769307, "compression_ratio": 1.7291666666666667, "no_speech_prob": 0.019321832805871964}, {"id": 55, "seek": 25938, "start": 264.71999999999997, "end": 267.71999999999997, "text": " and get another result.", "tokens": [50631, 293, 483, 1071, 1874, 13, 50781], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12602580278769307, "compression_ratio": 1.7291666666666667, "no_speech_prob": 0.019321832805871964}, {"id": 56, "seek": 25938, "start": 267.71999999999997, "end": 274.2, "text": " And just like anything, we can decide now to be better with stress or to be truthful", "tokens": [50781, 400, 445, 411, 1340, 11, 321, 393, 4536, 586, 281, 312, 1101, 365, 4244, 420, 281, 312, 44669, 51105], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12602580278769307, "compression_ratio": 1.7291666666666667, "no_speech_prob": 0.019321832805871964}, {"id": 57, "seek": 25938, "start": 274.2, "end": 279.08, "text": " with stress because stress is not the killer.", "tokens": [51105, 365, 4244, 570, 4244, 307, 406, 264, 13364, 13, 51349], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12602580278769307, "compression_ratio": 1.7291666666666667, "no_speech_prob": 0.019321832805871964}, {"id": 58, "seek": 25938, "start": 279.08, "end": 286.48, "text": " It's not a bad thing and it's not something that we shouldn't or can't go through.", "tokens": [51349, 467, 311, 406, 257, 1578, 551, 293, 309, 311, 406, 746, 300, 321, 4659, 380, 420, 393, 380, 352, 807, 13, 51719], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12602580278769307, "compression_ratio": 1.7291666666666667, "no_speech_prob": 0.019321832805871964}, {"id": 59, "seek": 28648, "start": 286.58000000000004, "end": 292.38, "text": " It's just a process of life that produces really good things.", "tokens": [50369, 467, 311, 445, 257, 1399, 295, 993, 300, 14725, 534, 665, 721, 13, 50659], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11337203979492187, "compression_ratio": 1.716279069767442, "no_speech_prob": 0.1630924493074417}, {"id": 60, "seek": 28648, "start": 292.38, "end": 297.06, "text": " And the reason why we call this mental fitness is because it's just like fitness.", "tokens": [50659, 400, 264, 1778, 983, 321, 818, 341, 4973, 15303, 307, 570, 309, 311, 445, 411, 15303, 13, 50893], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11337203979492187, "compression_ratio": 1.716279069767442, "no_speech_prob": 0.1630924493074417}, {"id": 61, "seek": 28648, "start": 297.06, "end": 304.06, "text": " When you work a muscle, you need to push against resistance in order to build muscle and to", "tokens": [50893, 1133, 291, 589, 257, 8679, 11, 291, 643, 281, 2944, 1970, 7335, 294, 1668, 281, 1322, 8679, 293, 281, 51243], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11337203979492187, "compression_ratio": 1.716279069767442, "no_speech_prob": 0.1630924493074417}, {"id": 62, "seek": 28648, "start": 304.06, "end": 306.90000000000003, "text": " increase strength, increase elasticity.", "tokens": [51243, 3488, 3800, 11, 3488, 46260, 13, 51385], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11337203979492187, "compression_ratio": 1.716279069767442, "no_speech_prob": 0.1630924493074417}, {"id": 63, "seek": 28648, "start": 306.90000000000003, "end": 313.62, "text": " You need to do things, you need to make actions, you need to be in mindset for your body, not", "tokens": [51385, 509, 643, 281, 360, 721, 11, 291, 643, 281, 652, 5909, 11, 291, 643, 281, 312, 294, 12543, 337, 428, 1772, 11, 406, 51721], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11337203979492187, "compression_ratio": 1.716279069767442, "no_speech_prob": 0.1630924493074417}, {"id": 64, "seek": 31362, "start": 313.62, "end": 317.76, "text": " against your body, in order to produce better health and better fitness.", "tokens": [50364, 1970, 428, 1772, 11, 294, 1668, 281, 5258, 1101, 1585, 293, 1101, 15303, 13, 50571], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.15025269841573324, "compression_ratio": 1.6018518518518519, "no_speech_prob": 0.014056283049285412}, {"id": 65, "seek": 31362, "start": 317.76, "end": 320.2, "text": " And it's actually the same mentally.", "tokens": [50571, 400, 309, 311, 767, 264, 912, 17072, 13, 50693], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.15025269841573324, "compression_ratio": 1.6018518518518519, "no_speech_prob": 0.014056283049285412}, {"id": 66, "seek": 31362, "start": 320.2, "end": 324.56, "text": " So essentially what we've done here, we've decided where you're at and where you want", "tokens": [50693, 407, 4476, 437, 321, 600, 1096, 510, 11, 321, 600, 3047, 689, 291, 434, 412, 293, 689, 291, 528, 50911], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.15025269841573324, "compression_ratio": 1.6018518518518519, "no_speech_prob": 0.014056283049285412}, {"id": 67, "seek": 31362, "start": 324.56, "end": 333.48, "text": " to go with this particular avenue of stress in writing, and you can choose to make a decision", "tokens": [50911, 281, 352, 365, 341, 1729, 39230, 295, 4244, 294, 3579, 11, 293, 291, 393, 2826, 281, 652, 257, 3537, 51357], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.15025269841573324, "compression_ratio": 1.6018518518518519, "no_speech_prob": 0.014056283049285412}, {"id": 68, "seek": 31362, "start": 333.48, "end": 339.72, "text": " to go forward with something more valuable to your goal.", "tokens": [51357, 281, 352, 2128, 365, 746, 544, 8263, 281, 428, 3387, 13, 51669], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.15025269841573324, "compression_ratio": 1.6018518518518519, "no_speech_prob": 0.014056283049285412}, {"id": 69, "seek": 33972, "start": 339.82000000000005, "end": 346.46000000000004, "text": " But in order to keep doing that, we need to have small practical practices to optimize", "tokens": [50369, 583, 294, 1668, 281, 1066, 884, 300, 11, 321, 643, 281, 362, 1359, 8496, 7525, 281, 19719, 50701], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11480242947498, "compression_ratio": 1.614678899082569, "no_speech_prob": 0.04625989496707916}, {"id": 70, "seek": 33972, "start": 346.46000000000004, "end": 354.04, "text": " and systematically go about training our muscles in our mind.", "tokens": [50701, 293, 39531, 352, 466, 3097, 527, 9530, 294, 527, 1575, 13, 51080], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11480242947498, "compression_ratio": 1.614678899082569, "no_speech_prob": 0.04625989496707916}, {"id": 71, "seek": 33972, "start": 354.04, "end": 359.14000000000004, "text": " So there's a few things that you can do to do that.", "tokens": [51080, 407, 456, 311, 257, 1326, 721, 300, 291, 393, 360, 281, 360, 300, 13, 51335], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11480242947498, "compression_ratio": 1.614678899082569, "no_speech_prob": 0.04625989496707916}, {"id": 72, "seek": 33972, "start": 359.14000000000004, "end": 363.58000000000004, "text": " And I like to call them micro stresses or purposeful stresses.", "tokens": [51335, 400, 286, 411, 281, 818, 552, 4532, 27732, 420, 4334, 906, 27732, 13, 51557], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11480242947498, "compression_ratio": 1.614678899082569, "no_speech_prob": 0.04625989496707916}, {"id": 73, "seek": 33972, "start": 363.58000000000004, "end": 368.66, "text": " So you're going to purposefully put yourself in an uncomfortable or a different position", "tokens": [51557, 407, 291, 434, 516, 281, 4334, 2277, 829, 1803, 294, 364, 10532, 420, 257, 819, 2535, 51811], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11480242947498, "compression_ratio": 1.614678899082569, "no_speech_prob": 0.04625989496707916}, {"id": 74, "seek": 36866, "start": 368.68, "end": 375.48, "text": " similar to a stretch or a lifting maneuver mentally in order to produce something better", "tokens": [50365, 2531, 281, 257, 5985, 420, 257, 15798, 25976, 17072, 294, 1668, 281, 5258, 746, 1101, 50705], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12620784759521483, "compression_ratio": 1.6129032258064515, "no_speech_prob": 0.0017904331907629967}, {"id": 75, "seek": 36866, "start": 375.48, "end": 378.24, "text": " for your whole life.", "tokens": [50705, 337, 428, 1379, 993, 13, 50843], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12620784759521483, "compression_ratio": 1.6129032258064515, "no_speech_prob": 0.0017904331907629967}, {"id": 76, "seek": 36866, "start": 378.24, "end": 382.44000000000005, "text": " So we're going to go through three examples of what you can do.", "tokens": [50843, 407, 321, 434, 516, 281, 352, 807, 1045, 5110, 295, 437, 291, 393, 360, 13, 51053], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12620784759521483, "compression_ratio": 1.6129032258064515, "no_speech_prob": 0.0017904331907629967}, {"id": 77, "seek": 36866, "start": 382.44000000000005, "end": 392.64000000000004, "text": " So number one, to deal with something physical about your body is you can do therapy on your", "tokens": [51053, 407, 1230, 472, 11, 281, 2028, 365, 746, 4001, 466, 428, 1772, 307, 291, 393, 360, 9492, 322, 428, 51563], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12620784759521483, "compression_ratio": 1.6129032258064515, "no_speech_prob": 0.0017904331907629967}, {"id": 78, "seek": 36866, "start": 392.64000000000004, "end": 397.0, "text": " body in the way of a cold shower.", "tokens": [51563, 1772, 294, 264, 636, 295, 257, 3554, 10128, 13, 51781], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12620784759521483, "compression_ratio": 1.6129032258064515, "no_speech_prob": 0.0017904331907629967}, {"id": 79, "seek": 39700, "start": 397.0, "end": 403.9, "text": " You can do exercise every day, which we're already is part of our program.", "tokens": [50364, 509, 393, 360, 5380, 633, 786, 11, 597, 321, 434, 1217, 307, 644, 295, 527, 1461, 13, 50709], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10550765104072038, "compression_ratio": 1.6232558139534883, "no_speech_prob": 0.0012302814284339547}, {"id": 80, "seek": 39700, "start": 403.9, "end": 408.18, "text": " And you can do something for your body that you know that it needs.", "tokens": [50709, 400, 291, 393, 360, 746, 337, 428, 1772, 300, 291, 458, 300, 309, 2203, 13, 50923], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10550765104072038, "compression_ratio": 1.6232558139534883, "no_speech_prob": 0.0012302814284339547}, {"id": 81, "seek": 39700, "start": 408.18, "end": 413.5, "text": " So either that's nutrition, therapy on an old injury, those kinds of things.", "tokens": [50923, 407, 2139, 300, 311, 14718, 11, 9492, 322, 364, 1331, 10454, 11, 729, 3685, 295, 721, 13, 51189], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10550765104072038, "compression_ratio": 1.6232558139534883, "no_speech_prob": 0.0012302814284339547}, {"id": 82, "seek": 39700, "start": 413.5, "end": 417.82, "text": " If you commit to one of those things for your physical body, then you can change your mental", "tokens": [51189, 759, 291, 5599, 281, 472, 295, 729, 721, 337, 428, 4001, 1772, 11, 550, 291, 393, 1319, 428, 4973, 51405], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10550765104072038, "compression_ratio": 1.6232558139534883, "no_speech_prob": 0.0012302814284339547}, {"id": 83, "seek": 39700, "start": 417.82, "end": 421.74, "text": " state about the particular stresses.", "tokens": [51405, 1785, 466, 264, 1729, 27732, 13, 51601], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10550765104072038, "compression_ratio": 1.6232558139534883, "no_speech_prob": 0.0012302814284339547}, {"id": 84, "seek": 42174, "start": 421.74, "end": 427.56, "text": " Most of the time when people don't go to physical therapy for something physical, it's because", "tokens": [50364, 4534, 295, 264, 565, 562, 561, 500, 380, 352, 281, 4001, 9492, 337, 746, 4001, 11, 309, 311, 570, 50655], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1158667802810669, "compression_ratio": 1.8087649402390438, "no_speech_prob": 0.1282213032245636}, {"id": 85, "seek": 42174, "start": 427.56, "end": 429.98, "text": " they don't want to be uncomfortable with the pain.", "tokens": [50655, 436, 500, 380, 528, 281, 312, 10532, 365, 264, 1822, 13, 50776], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1158667802810669, "compression_ratio": 1.8087649402390438, "no_speech_prob": 0.1282213032245636}, {"id": 86, "seek": 42174, "start": 429.98, "end": 434.86, "text": " But what it really does is it elongates the pain to be longer and bug them for a longer", "tokens": [50776, 583, 437, 309, 534, 775, 307, 309, 40786, 1024, 264, 1822, 281, 312, 2854, 293, 7426, 552, 337, 257, 2854, 51020], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1158667802810669, "compression_ratio": 1.8087649402390438, "no_speech_prob": 0.1282213032245636}, {"id": 87, "seek": 42174, "start": 434.86, "end": 436.18, "text": " time in their life.", "tokens": [51020, 565, 294, 641, 993, 13, 51086], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1158667802810669, "compression_ratio": 1.8087649402390438, "no_speech_prob": 0.1282213032245636}, {"id": 88, "seek": 42174, "start": 436.18, "end": 438.28000000000003, "text": " And we do the same thing mentally.", "tokens": [51086, 400, 321, 360, 264, 912, 551, 17072, 13, 51191], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1158667802810669, "compression_ratio": 1.8087649402390438, "no_speech_prob": 0.1282213032245636}, {"id": 89, "seek": 42174, "start": 438.28000000000003, "end": 442.34000000000003, "text": " So go after it, get after it, do something physical for your body for the sake of the", "tokens": [51191, 407, 352, 934, 309, 11, 483, 934, 309, 11, 360, 746, 4001, 337, 428, 1772, 337, 264, 9717, 295, 264, 51394], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1158667802810669, "compression_ratio": 1.8087649402390438, "no_speech_prob": 0.1282213032245636}, {"id": 90, "seek": 42174, "start": 442.34000000000003, "end": 443.34000000000003, "text": " mental.", "tokens": [51394, 4973, 13, 51444], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1158667802810669, "compression_ratio": 1.8087649402390438, "no_speech_prob": 0.1282213032245636}, {"id": 91, "seek": 42174, "start": 443.34000000000003, "end": 450.34000000000003, "text": " So that's cold showers, exercise every day, or a therapy for your body.", "tokens": [51444, 407, 300, 311, 3554, 29499, 11, 5380, 633, 786, 11, 420, 257, 9492, 337, 428, 1772, 13, 51794], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1158667802810669, "compression_ratio": 1.8087649402390438, "no_speech_prob": 0.1282213032245636}, {"id": 92, "seek": 45034, "start": 450.34, "end": 455.09999999999997, "text": " And that could even be something like stretching if you would if you prefer mentally to separate", "tokens": [50364, 400, 300, 727, 754, 312, 746, 411, 19632, 498, 291, 576, 498, 291, 4382, 17072, 281, 4994, 50602], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1334686146842109, "compression_ratio": 1.6298342541436464, "no_speech_prob": 0.00499610835686326}, {"id": 93, "seek": 45034, "start": 455.09999999999997, "end": 457.29999999999995, "text": " stretching from exercise.", "tokens": [50602, 19632, 490, 5380, 13, 50712], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1334686146842109, "compression_ratio": 1.6298342541436464, "no_speech_prob": 0.00499610835686326}, {"id": 94, "seek": 45034, "start": 457.29999999999995, "end": 465.17999999999995, "text": " So that's that's a really easy, tangible starting point for you to go because it's so it's so", "tokens": [50712, 407, 300, 311, 300, 311, 257, 534, 1858, 11, 27094, 2891, 935, 337, 291, 281, 352, 570, 309, 311, 370, 309, 311, 370, 51106], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1334686146842109, "compression_ratio": 1.6298342541436464, "no_speech_prob": 0.00499610835686326}, {"id": 95, "seek": 45034, "start": 465.17999999999995, "end": 469.21999999999997, "text": " easy to measure on your on your physical person.", "tokens": [51106, 1858, 281, 3481, 322, 428, 322, 428, 4001, 954, 13, 51308], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1334686146842109, "compression_ratio": 1.6298342541436464, "no_speech_prob": 0.00499610835686326}, {"id": 96, "seek": 45034, "start": 469.21999999999997, "end": 472.17999999999995, "text": " Number two, something social.", "tokens": [51308, 5118, 732, 11, 746, 2093, 13, 51456], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1334686146842109, "compression_ratio": 1.6298342541436464, "no_speech_prob": 0.00499610835686326}, {"id": 97, "seek": 47218, "start": 472.18, "end": 480.5, "text": " So for example, if you are talkative, you can choose once a week, you are going to spend", "tokens": [50364, 407, 337, 1365, 11, 498, 291, 366, 751, 1166, 11, 291, 393, 2826, 1564, 257, 1243, 11, 291, 366, 516, 281, 3496, 50780], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09746037210736956, "compression_ratio": 1.7024390243902439, "no_speech_prob": 0.02045672945678234}, {"id": 98, "seek": 47218, "start": 480.5, "end": 489.66, "text": " 10 minutes listening to somebody very, very actively and intensively to stretch your ability", "tokens": [50780, 1266, 2077, 4764, 281, 2618, 588, 11, 588, 13022, 293, 18957, 356, 281, 5985, 428, 3485, 51238], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09746037210736956, "compression_ratio": 1.7024390243902439, "no_speech_prob": 0.02045672945678234}, {"id": 99, "seek": 47218, "start": 489.66, "end": 494.62, "text": " to deal with your strengths and weaknesses in your mind.", "tokens": [51238, 281, 2028, 365, 428, 16986, 293, 24381, 294, 428, 1575, 13, 51486], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09746037210736956, "compression_ratio": 1.7024390243902439, "no_speech_prob": 0.02045672945678234}, {"id": 100, "seek": 47218, "start": 494.62, "end": 500.34000000000003, "text": " If you're less talkative, maybe you want to stretch your ability by being the one sharing", "tokens": [51486, 759, 291, 434, 1570, 751, 1166, 11, 1310, 291, 528, 281, 5985, 428, 3485, 538, 885, 264, 472, 5414, 51772], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09746037210736956, "compression_ratio": 1.7024390243902439, "no_speech_prob": 0.02045672945678234}, {"id": 101, "seek": 47218, "start": 500.34000000000003, "end": 501.42, "text": " with another person.", "tokens": [51772, 365, 1071, 954, 13, 51826], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09746037210736956, "compression_ratio": 1.7024390243902439, "no_speech_prob": 0.02045672945678234}, {"id": 102, "seek": 50142, "start": 501.46000000000004, "end": 506.54, "text": " So once a week, you can spend 10 minutes talking to a stranger, talking to your spouse, talking", "tokens": [50366, 407, 1564, 257, 1243, 11, 291, 393, 3496, 1266, 2077, 1417, 281, 257, 18834, 11, 1417, 281, 428, 23013, 11, 1417, 50620], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.15272581100463867, "compression_ratio": 1.639676113360324, "no_speech_prob": 0.04947112128138542}, {"id": 103, "seek": 50142, "start": 506.54, "end": 512.78, "text": " to someone else, a friend, and interacting in a way that's going to stretch you mentally.", "tokens": [50620, 281, 1580, 1646, 11, 257, 1277, 11, 293, 18017, 294, 257, 636, 300, 311, 516, 281, 5985, 291, 17072, 13, 50932], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.15272581100463867, "compression_ratio": 1.639676113360324, "no_speech_prob": 0.04947112128138542}, {"id": 104, "seek": 50142, "start": 512.78, "end": 517.3000000000001, "text": " The point is to get out of your comfort zone, okay?", "tokens": [50932, 440, 935, 307, 281, 483, 484, 295, 428, 3400, 6668, 11, 1392, 30, 51158], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.15272581100463867, "compression_ratio": 1.639676113360324, "no_speech_prob": 0.04947112128138542}, {"id": 105, "seek": 50142, "start": 517.3000000000001, "end": 522.82, "text": " And then number three is to do something personally or individually with your body.", "tokens": [51158, 400, 550, 1230, 1045, 307, 281, 360, 746, 5665, 420, 16652, 365, 428, 1772, 13, 51434], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.15272581100463867, "compression_ratio": 1.639676113360324, "no_speech_prob": 0.04947112128138542}, {"id": 106, "seek": 50142, "start": 522.82, "end": 528.74, "text": " So that can be even the meditation we did two weeks ago before you get on and ride.", "tokens": [51434, 407, 300, 393, 312, 754, 264, 12537, 321, 630, 732, 3259, 2057, 949, 291, 483, 322, 293, 5077, 13, 51730], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.15272581100463867, "compression_ratio": 1.639676113360324, "no_speech_prob": 0.04947112128138542}, {"id": 107, "seek": 52874, "start": 528.74, "end": 535.5, "text": " It could be something you do in the morning where you wake up and you set yourself up", "tokens": [50364, 467, 727, 312, 746, 291, 360, 294, 264, 2446, 689, 291, 6634, 493, 293, 291, 992, 1803, 493, 50702], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11191525751230669, "compression_ratio": 1.75, "no_speech_prob": 0.03384239226579666}, {"id": 108, "seek": 52874, "start": 535.5, "end": 540.1, "text": " for the day mentally, a state of mind that you want to put yourself in, those kinds of", "tokens": [50702, 337, 264, 786, 17072, 11, 257, 1785, 295, 1575, 300, 291, 528, 281, 829, 1803, 294, 11, 729, 3685, 295, 50932], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11191525751230669, "compression_ratio": 1.75, "no_speech_prob": 0.03384239226579666}, {"id": 109, "seek": 52874, "start": 540.1, "end": 545.1800000000001, "text": " things that are personal and individual, and it just involves you.", "tokens": [50932, 721, 300, 366, 2973, 293, 2609, 11, 293, 309, 445, 11626, 291, 13, 51186], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11191525751230669, "compression_ratio": 1.75, "no_speech_prob": 0.03384239226579666}, {"id": 110, "seek": 52874, "start": 545.1800000000001, "end": 551.74, "text": " So those are some very, very broad examples of you putting micro stresses on yourself", "tokens": [51186, 407, 729, 366, 512, 588, 11, 588, 4152, 5110, 295, 291, 3372, 4532, 27732, 322, 1803, 51514], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11191525751230669, "compression_ratio": 1.75, "no_speech_prob": 0.03384239226579666}, {"id": 111, "seek": 52874, "start": 551.74, "end": 557.7, "text": " to help work the mental muscle of your mind so they can serve you in your life and your", "tokens": [51514, 281, 854, 589, 264, 4973, 8679, 295, 428, 1575, 370, 436, 393, 4596, 291, 294, 428, 993, 293, 428, 51812], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11191525751230669, "compression_ratio": 1.75, "no_speech_prob": 0.03384239226579666}, {"id": 112, "seek": 55770, "start": 557.7, "end": 561.58, "text": " goals even better than it already is.", "tokens": [50364, 5493, 754, 1101, 813, 309, 1217, 307, 13, 50558], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.2536239831343941, "compression_ratio": 1.0273972602739727, "no_speech_prob": 0.06541197746992111}, {"id": 113, "seek": 55770, "start": 561.58, "end": 563.1800000000001, "text": " As always, for the sake of the horse.", "tokens": [50558, 1018, 1009, 11, 337, 264, 9717, 295, 264, 6832, 13, 50638], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.2536239831343941, "compression_ratio": 1.0273972602739727, "no_speech_prob": 0.06541197746992111}], "language": "en"}